title: Manchester United set for 4,266-mile round-trip after drawing Rostov in the Europa League last-16 after breezing past St Etienne in the previous round
text:
EFL To Russia with love Manchester United set for 4,266-mile round-trip after drawing Rostov in the Europa League last-16 after breezing past St Etienne in the previous round 
Jose Mourinho's side thumped Ligue 1 side 4-0 in the last-32, but should now face a sterner test against the Russian outfit By Dave Fraser
